{"id":554821,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/03/【对比新闻】五星红旗背后的雪山狮子旗/","date":"2017-03-24T07:19:37Z","modified":"2017-03-24T07:20:24Z","title":"【对比新闻】五星红旗背后的雪山狮子旗","content":"<p>李克强于当地时间2017年3月24日抵达澳洲悉尼，<strong>亲中华媒里永远是一片和谐</strong>：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_554814\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/今日悉尼.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-554814\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/今日悉尼.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"507\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/今日悉尼.jpg 1332w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/今日悉尼-300x277.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/今日悉尼-768x708.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/今日悉尼-1024x944.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">微博截图</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_554813\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/亿忆澳洲.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-554813\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/亿忆澳洲.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"485\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/亿忆澳洲.jpg 1328w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/亿忆澳洲-300x265.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/亿忆澳洲-768x678.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/亿忆澳洲-1024x904.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">微博截图</span></p></div>\n<p><strong>然而从以下图片可以看出，在悉尼市中心李克强下榻的酒店外，自由西藏示威者与亲中华人组织的距离非常之近，雪山狮子旗与中国国旗常常同时出镜：</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/C7qNHQkUwAEiBlH.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-554816\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/C7qNHQk